---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Members" description="Member resources for American Legion Country Club, including the ALCC Ladies.">
  <PageHero title="Members" subtitle="Resources and updates for ALCC members." />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid--2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>ALCC Ladies</h3>
            <p>In the annals of American Legion Country Club, the mark
            left by our devoted lady golfers is impossible to overlook.
            Their camaraderie and enthusiasm for the sport illuminate each
            day at the club. This committed group gathers every Wednesday
            evening for the Ladies' League, and their involvement extends
            to courses throughout the region. Their dedication is evident
            in their active role at the club, including running the food
            stand at the Annual June Invitational — raising funds for
            their organization while contributing to the golf course in
            diverse ways.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__body">
            <h3>Members Exchange</h3>
            <p>A space for member classifieds and exchanges. This section
            isn't published yet on the current site — add current listings
            here in <code>src/pages/members.astro</code>, or link out to a
            shared document, once the club is ready to use it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:2rem;">Questions about your membership? <a href="/contact">Contact the club office</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
